      <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5"><tr><td><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font face="Tolk, Times, serif" class="h1font">Servant of the Secret Fire</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"> | <A HREF="/lotr/decks/decks.php?reviews=20174">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=3899">Hartman "Moff Hart" Andersen</A></FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"> Has won two tournaments (including Chase the Can).  Powerful Combos: Gandalf and Servant of Secret Fire with Uruk Hai and Worry and Ulaire Enquea.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"> December 22, 2001</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont"> Starting:<br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(173)">Frodo, Old Bilbo&#39;s Heir</a><br>
